column2: "Speaking of which, I completely forgot to ask you, who is it you're searching for?"
"Oh, you mean Camarotz? He's a handsome guy, looks a lot like me."
"You can stop it with the narcissism."
"Did you look at me for a specific reason just now?"
"Camarotz, I guess you'd say he's my pair."
"He left one day and never came back, so I just started looking for him."
"He might have been attacked by an enemy, who knows? There are a lot of dangerous things out there."
"Like getting attacked by a crazy girl with a giant sword or something!"
"I uh, sorry. I'm really sorry about that."
"But I'm helping you look, so we're even now, right?"
"Even? You're forcing your help on me."
"Do people ever tell you you're a self centered control freak?"
